===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{statistics}} A [[graphical]] [[display]] of [[numerical]] data in the form of upright bars, with the [[area]] of each bar representing [[frequency]].

====Usage notes====
The data on the horizontal axis need not be numerical, but can be any property such as colour.  Only the frequency need be numerical.<br>
Histograms are sometimes drawn with the bars horizontal.

